   "In the end we will conserve only what we love; we will love only what
   we understand; and we will understand only what we are taught."
   Baba Dioum,
   Senegalese ecologist
     __________________________________________________________________

    Education, whether formal or informal, is what enables people to make
    informed decisions about the world in which they live. Education is
    vital for conserving life in our oceans, which is why the Sanctuary
    programs aim to enlighten and excite.

